<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.6.1">
<l>kācuṅ kaṟaiyuṭaik kūṟaikku maṅkōrkaṟ ṟaikku</l>
<l>mācai yiṉālaṅka vattap pēriṭu mātarkāḷ</l>
<l>kēcavaṉ pēriṭ ṭunīṅkaḷtē ṉittiru miṉō</l>
<l>nāyakaṉ nāraṇaṉ tamaṉṉai narakam pukāḷ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You fools who give [your children] useless names</l>
<l rend="indent">because of desire for stained clothes, coins,</l>
<l rend="indent">and a handful of grain!</l>
<l>Give the name Kesava [and] you will be happy!</l>
<l>The mother of [a] Nāyaka Nāraṇa will not go to hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
